lct - Local configuration tool

Usage:
  lct COMMAND
  lct [COMMAND] --help | -h
  lct --version | -v

Commands:
  lib           Manage lct libraries
  env           Manage local environment variables
  plugin        Develop and manage lct plugins
  alias         Manage lct aliases
  dotfiles      Manage dotfiles list
  configs       Manage configs list
  init          Initialize lct configuration
  bootstrap     Bootstrap your local configuration
  completions   Generate bash completions
  config        Open your config files in your nvim
  setup         Setup lct in your shell
  gather        Gather local configuration files
  prune         Prune config and plugins files

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number
